Base URL: https://api.yourdomain.com/v1

Authentication:
├── POST   /auth/register
├── POST   /auth/login
├── POST   /auth/logout
├── POST   /auth/refresh
├── POST   /auth/forgot-password
└── POST   /auth/reset-password

Users:
├── GET    /users/me
├── PUT    /users/me
├── DELETE /users/me
└── GET    /users/me/preferences

Organizations:
├── GET    /organizations
├── POST   /organizations
├── GET    /organizations/{id}
├── PUT    /organizations/{id}
├── DELETE /organizations/{id}
├── GET    /organizations/{id}/members
├── POST   /organizations/{id}/members
└── DELETE /organizations/{id}/members/{user_id}

Data Sources:
├── GET    /data-sources
├── POST   /data-sources
├── GET    /data-sources/{id}
├── PUT    /data-sources/{id}
├── DELETE /data-sources/{id}
├── POST   /data-sources/{id}/test-connection
├── POST   /data-sources/{id}/sync
├── GET    /data-sources/{id}/schema
├── GET    /data-sources/{id}/preview
└── GET    /data-sources/{id}/statistics

Dashboards:
├── GET    /dashboards
├── POST   /dashboards
├── GET    /dashboards/{id}
├── PUT    /dashboards/{id}
├── DELETE /dashboards/{id}
├── POST   /dashboards/{id}/duplicate
├── POST   /dashboards/{id}/share
├── GET    /dashboards/{id}/export?format=pdf|png|json
├── POST   /dashboards/generate (Auto-generate)
└── GET    /dashboards/templates

Widgets:
├── GET    /dashboards/{dashboard_id}/widgets
├── POST   /dashboards/{dashboard_id}/widgets
├── GET    /widgets/{id}
├── PUT    /widgets/{id}
├── DELETE /widgets/{id}
├── GET    /widgets/{id}/data
└── POST   /widgets/{id}/refresh

Insights:
├── GET    /dashboards/{id}/insights
├── POST   /dashboards/{id}/insights/generate
├── GET    /insights/{id}
└── DELETE /insights/{id}

Analytics:
├── POST   /analytics/query (NLP query)
├── GET    /analytics/forecast?metric=...&periods=...
├── GET    /analytics/correlation?metrics[]=...
└── GET    /analytics/anomalies?threshold=...

Alerts:
├── GET    /alerts
├── POST   /alerts
├── GET    /alerts/{id}
├── PUT    /alerts/{id}
├── DELETE /alerts/{id}
└── GET    /alerts/history

Export:
├── POST   /export/dashboard/{id}?format=pdf
├── POST   /export/widget/{id}?format=png
└── GET    /export/jobs/{job_id}/status

Admin:
├── GET    /admin/usage-stats
├── GET    /admin/audit-logs
└── GET    /admin/system-health

WebSocket:
└── WS     /ws/realtime?token=...